Description_lang: Increases the range of your Demonic Gateway by $s1 yards, and reduces the cast time by $s2%. Reduces the time between how often players can take your Demonic Gateway by $s3 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Increases the range of your Demonic Gateway by 20 yards, and reduces the cast time by 30%. Reduces the time between how often players can take your Demonic Gateway by 30 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta 20 m el alcance de tu Portal demoníaco y reduce un 30% su tiempo de lanzamiento. Reduce 30 s el tiempo que los jugadores deben esperar entre los usos de tu Portal demoníaco.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em 20 m o alcance do seu Portal Demoníaco e reduz em 30% o tempo de lançamento dele. Reduz em30 s o tempo de espera para que jogadores possam usar o seu Portal Demoníaco.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die Reichweite von 'Dämonisches Tor' um 20 Meter und verringert die Zauberzeit um 30%. Verringert die Zeitabstände, in denen Spielercharaktere Euer 'Dämonisches Tor' nutzen können, um 30 Sek.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases the range of your Demonic Gateway by 20 yards, and reduces the cast time by 30%. Reduces the time between how often players can take your Demonic Gateway by 30 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta 20 m el alcance de tu portal demoníaco y reduce un 30% su tiempo de lanzamiento. Reduce 30 s el tiempo que tienen que esperar los jugadores para volver a utilizar tu portal demoníaco.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente la portée de Porte des démons de 20 m et réduit son temps d’incantation de 30 %. Réduit le délai avant lequel les personnages-joueurs peuvent l’emprunter à nouveau de 30 s.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la portata di Varco Demoniaco di 20 m e ne riduce il tempo di lancio del 30%. Riduce l'intervallo di attesa prima di poter riutilizzare il varco di 30 s.
description_blz.ru_RU: Увеличивает дальность действия "Демонических врат" на 20 м и сокращает время применения на 30%. Уменьшает промежуток времени до повторного использования врат игроками на 30 сек.
description_blz.ko_KR: 악마의 관문의 사거리가 20미터만큼 증가하고, 시전 시간이 30%만큼 감소합니다. 악마의 관문을 이용할 수 있는 대기시간이 30초만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的惡魔之門範圍延長20碼，施法時間縮短30%。此外，玩家使用惡魔之門的間隔時間縮短30秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 使你的恶魔传送门的射程延长20码，施法时间缩短30%并使玩家使用你的恶魔传送门的间隔时间缩短30秒。
